## 7. Router Port Forwarding

### 7.1 Required inbound forwards
On your perimeter router/firewall, forward:
- TCP `80` -> `<unraid-lan-ip>:80` (SWAG)
- TCP `443` -> `<unraid-lan-ip>:443` (SWAG)

### 7.2 DNS records
At your DNS provider, create/update:
- `A` record for `smc-projects.com` -> your public IP
- `A` record for `www.smc-projects.com` -> your public IP

### 7.3 Security rules
- Do not forward `3000` or `8000` publicly.
- Restrict Unraid admin UI exposure from WAN.
- If possible, manage Unraid UI only from LAN or VPN.

### 7.4 External test checklist
From a network outside your LAN:
1. `https://smc-projects.com` returns frontend.
2. `https://smc-projects.com/api/health/` returns healthy response.
3. TLS certificate is valid and trusted.

